dc_title_s: Alternative Fuel Filling Stations: United States, 2015
dc_description_s: This point dataset shows the locations of alternative fuel filling stations in the United States for 2015. This layer is a part of a collection of GIS data containing renewable and electric energy information for the U.S., including data on transmission lines, power plants and electricity substations.This shapefile can be used to locate alternative fuel filling stations in the United States.
